/target

# Cargo.lock is committed even though this is a library crate. `librustpivx`
# pulls in `core2 ^0.3` as a transitive dep, and every published 0.3.x has
# been yanked — any fresh resolution fails. Keeping the lockfile pins the
# yanked version (which is still downloadable), so CI and fresh clones can
# build without manual `[patch.crates-io]` gymnastics.
